\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 No. On - only with the boarding house, well he didn't work hard then, not - not working about is it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 You had people more or less all the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Your mother was about twenty when you were born, where did she come from?
