My mother and father used to sleep on the - ground floor in the other house. And - we used to sleep up the - we - we all slept in the same house but we sort of - children were sent upstairs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Can you remember what the house was exactly like, you had a parlour, middle room and kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Yes.
