\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 That's it. Only ordinary housework.
