\insrsid4217081\charrsid4983030 ning, for the men, get the men\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 
 breakfast, my father used to do the cooking for the men. And - the - mind he wouldn't let my mother get up in the morning. She - he used to let}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4217081\charrsid4983030  her stay in bed you know \endash  \lquote til}{
