\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Your father would organize it would he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 A street outing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 When would you go, would it be on a Bank Holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 On Bank - generally in August.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 What about the other Bank Holidays, Whitsun or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Well - the church schools, we used to go to church outings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Did you ever go away for a holiday?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Not on my own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Did you go with anyone when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 What about Saturdays in those days, could you tell me how you spent Saturdays when you were a little girl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 
Well, mostly - when - when we were small it was mostly around the street that was all, we couldn't go far but - you couldn't - go anywhere far unless we got into where - there used to be a park down here in the square. Lived up the top by a church, by St
 Mary's church we used to live. We could go down the park but - nowhere else, sometimes we would go to Higher Gardens of a Saturday. Children all together. Nowhere else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 What about Sundays, you mentioned you went to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Oh three times on a Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Did you have different clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Always had different clothes for Sunday, we'd Sunday clothes and boots.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Did you play games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Not on a Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Did your parents think it wrong to work or play on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Yes. Wouldn't play. No. Mother couldn't do no cleaning on a Sunday. Well you could sweep, but no scrubbing or nothing like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Did your parents attend a place of worship or not? You mentioned your father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 My father, my mother didn't go much, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 It was the Baptist?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Father was a Baptist.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Would he go often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Every Sunday.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 How often Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Well in his late years he would go three times on a Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 What about when you were children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Oh when we were children, oh he used to go every Sunday, sometimes I'd take - go with him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Would he go in the morning or the night or the afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Oh afternoon. Afternoon and night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 You went to Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 There were Sunday school outings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 What were they like, where would you go on the Sunday school outings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Oh, well mostly out - fields out - fields outside the - \{BLANK\} or somewhere along there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 In Cardiff?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Yes. Wouldn't go very far like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 What other social activities organised by the chapel did you take part in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 None really on my own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Was there a choir, did you belong to a choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 I used to sing in the mission - they had a choir in the mission - Anthony Street mission. Choir.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 How often would you go there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Every Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 You'd go there in addition to the Baptist chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Did the chapel run a temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Well I didn't used to go to the chapel really, I used to - nor my father didn't go the Baptist chapel, he used t
o go to the chapel that was down here before this one was built. Wesleyan.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 It's a Congregational now isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Yes. Welsey - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 That's where you used to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 That's where.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 There was no Baptist down here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 No. Used to go there. But I used to go to St Mary's.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 The church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Yes. I was born and - I was baptized at St Mary's and married there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 What about when you were a little girl, where would you go on Sunday, what place of worship?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 I used to go to St Mary's.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 So your father and you wouldn't go to the same place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 No. St Thomas's - in the evening I might go with him to the Wesleyan like - but - once in a way, but we would mostly go to St Mary's.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 That's Church of England?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Church of England. My mother was Church of England.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Did you belong to the choir in the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 No, I - I used to go the - mission hall sometimes you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 What did they do, what did the choir do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Oh they'd have on the - on a platform singing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Did you belong to any other club being organised by the church, would there be a temperance club there?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Band of Hope we used to call it. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Did you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 What sort of things would they do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Well - play games and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Were you a member?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Yes. Band of Hope.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Was grace said at meals in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 By whom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 My father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Did you ever have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Only when my father'd read the Bible to us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 When would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 In the night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Would he often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Mostly in the evenings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Did your father take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Oh I don't think so, he wasn't much bothered.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Do you know what his views were?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 I never know whether - now if he voted I don't know whoever he voted for.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 No idea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 No. He wouldn't say anyhow. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Do you remember your father voting in a general election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Yes, I remember him voting but he would never tell you who he voted for.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 What about your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Oh I don't think she voted much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Did she ever vote?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Yes, she used to vote, but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Any idea what she'd vote for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 I think it was a Liberal that time if I'm not mistaken. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 They'd vote Liberal would they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 You don't know about your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 He wouldn't tell you what he voted for.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 He wouldn't talk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 In some places at that time men felt they risked losing their job or their h
ouse if they voted differently from their employers, do you know if your father felt himself under that kind of pressure?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 He didn't have an employer really did he because he was keeping a boarding house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6162818 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8550931 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11796586\charrsid4983030 Was your father a member of a political party?
